<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Synotis nayongensis in the wild (Luzui village, Nayong, Guizhou, China). A habitat B habit C portion of vegetative stem D leaf blades from the adaxil view E synflorescence F portion of synflorescence (side view, note the white phyllaries with green apex, and also note the white pappus). Scale bars: 5 mm (C); 6 mm (F)." , "Figure 4. Record of Synotis panzhouensis." , "Figure 2. Synotis panzhouensis in the wild (Dazhai village, Panzhou, Guizhou, China). A habitat B general habit C portion of vegetative stem D leaf blades (left two: adaxial surface; right four: abaxial surface) E synflorescence F capitulum (top view) G capitulum (side view) H a disk floret with red-purple pappus. Scale bars: 5 mm (C); 10 cm (D); 4 mm (F); 1 cm (G, H)." , "Figure 1. Holotype of Synotis panzhouensis (Panzhou, Guizhou, China, Z. Li & M. Tang 2020 - 0901 (JXAU ))." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/469165" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/469166" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/469164" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/469163" .

